precis:
Amendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS Schedule No. 883 providing
for the use of the "maltogenic amylase" enzyme in the hydrolysis of edible
starches for the production of dextrins, maltose, glucose and glucose
solids, as well as to delay staling in bread and bakery products.
